query:
SELECT ts.name,
                        ts."timestamp",
                        ARRAY[]::varchar[] AS members,
                        ARRAY[]::integer[] AS frosh,
                        ts.approved
                    FROM technical_seminars ts
                    LEFT JOIN freshman_seminar_attendance fsa ON
                        fsa.seminar_id = ts.id
                    WHERE ts.approved
                    AND timestamp > $1::timestamp
                    AND fsa.fid = $2::int4
